# Design Review Reports

This directory contains design review reports generated by the `/review-story` workflow.

**Report Format**: `design-review-{YYYY-MM-DD}-{story-id}.md`

**Example**: `design-review-2026-03-01-e01-s03.md`

Reports include:
- Visual consistency findings
- Accessibility violations (WCAG 2.1 AA)
- Responsive design issues
- Design system adherence
- Screenshots from Playwright MCP testing
